aysages alternant avec des fleurons. Contre-\u00e9mail peint d\u0027un port. Pendant orn\u00e9 de feuilles. Cadran \u00e0 chiffres romains, au centre, Mars et V\u00e9nus ; sur un cercle rapport\u00e9 sont grav\u00e9s des chiffres arabes (minutes). Echappement \u00e0 roue de rencontre, fus\u00e9e avec cha\u00eene. La rosette de r\u00e9glage ainsi que le coq, grav\u00e9 et reperc\u00e9, sont en argent. Plaque ajour\u00e9e et grav\u00e9e appliqu\u00e9e autour du carr\u00e9 de remontage.","inscriptions":"","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"5,4","displayDimension":"5,4 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Diam\u00e8tre","value":"4","displayDimension":"4 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Epaisseur","value":"2,1","displayDimension":"2,1 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : laiton\r\nMat\u00e9riau : or\r\nTechnique : techniques m\u00e9tal (orf\u00e8vrerie)\r\nTechnique : \u00e9maill\u00e9 = \u00e9maillage = \u00e9mail = \u00e9maux (techniques m\u00e9tal)","placeOfCreation":"Gen\u00e8ve (Europe-\u003ESuisse) (bo\u00eetier) ; Londres (Grande-Bretagne = Grande Bretagne-\u003EAngleterre) (mouvement)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Collection Claudius C\u00f4te (1881-1956), Lyon ; legs Mme Marie-Fran\u00e7oise C\u00f4te, accept\u00e9 par d\u00e9cret du 9 juillet 1961","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Mme C\u00f4te, Marie-Fran\u00e7oise","note":"","role":", Donateur"},{"value":"M. C\u00f4te, Claudius","note":"","role":", Collectionneur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"legs","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date du legs","value":"1961","startYear":1961,"endYear":1961},{"type":"date de comit\u00e9\/commission","value":"02\/02\/1961",